{"data":[{"date":"22:01 25/07","title":"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 gi\u1eefa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i v\u00e0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/hlv-chu-dinh-nghiem-giai-thich-su-ky-gio-giua-ha-noi-va-binh-duong.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 c\u00f3 l\u00fac b\u1ecb d\u1eabn 1-3 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u1ee7a HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam khi t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 Oseni, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tho\u00e1t thua v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 3-3.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_0887.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 khi\u1ebfn B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng lu\u00f4n g\u00e2y ra kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i lu\u00f4n g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 khi ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: &quot;Do s\u1ef1 k\u1ef5 gi\u01a1 gi\u1eefa hai c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau lu\u00f4n \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t m\u00e1u l\u1eeda v\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ganh \u0111ua. B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Nh\u01b0ng B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng con ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i c\u1ea7m nh\u1ecbp t\u1ed1t, V\u0103n V\u0169 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao c\u00f2n Ti\u1ebfn Linh l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ed1t. C\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n qua h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7, t\u1eeb d\u01b0\u1edbi ph\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng l\u00ean th\u00ec H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u1eaft, c\u00f2n B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 lu\u00e2n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong b\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 tu\u1ed5i U23 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean theo HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diem yeu lon nhat cua Do Hung Dung la luon lam nen cho nguoi khac.\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/IMG_0996.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n&quot;V\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i th\u00ec H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu, lu\u00f4n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u cho \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn&quot; - V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: &quot;T\u01b0 duy chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u1ee7a D\u0169ng r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng pha D\u0169ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngay nh\u01b0ng lu\u00f4n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch nh\u01b0ng HLV Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam cho r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed9i chia \u0111\u1ec1u cho c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018 cho \u0111\u1ebfn nay v\u1eabn \u0111ang th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 90% m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 gi\u1eefa B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng vs H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 17h00 ng\u00e0y 5/9.<br />\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018:</h2>\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/gay-kho-khan-cho-ha-noi-hlv-tran-minh-chien-giau-bai-291-192025.html\">G\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV Tr\u1ea7n Minh Chi\u1ebfn gi\u1ea5u b\u00e0i cho tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/ha-noi-vs-binh-duong-ban-ket-cup-quoc-gia-viet-nam-2018-372-191996.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 3-3 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (KT): L\u1ea1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng tho\u00e1t thua, CLB Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-20-vleague-su-vo-doi-cua-ha-noi-168-191828.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 20 V-League: S\u1ef1 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-ha-noi-tuyen-bo-tu-tin-sau-tran-thang-thanh-hoa-168-191784.html\">HLV H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1ef1 tin sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Thanh H\u00f3a</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thua-nguoc-clb-ha-noi-hlv-flc-thanh-hoa-phai-thua-nhan-mot-su-that-168-191753.html\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HLV FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/thanh-hoa-vs-ha-noi-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191730.html\">Thanh H\u00f3a 2-3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1634","checkdouble":"192030"},{"date":"22:50 25/07","title":"Man United b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba\u201d c\u1ee7a Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/man-united-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-nguoi-thua-cua-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, CLB Man United \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</h2><h2>Man United mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7&nbsp;<span style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry</span><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Mina</span></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man United mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man United mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina c\u1ee7a Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/Man-United-muon-chieu-mo-trung-ve-Yerry-Mina-cua-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Man United mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina&nbsp;t\u1eeb Barca</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina gia nh\u1eadp CLB Barcelona t\u1eeb CLB Palmeiras h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Nou Camp kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o v\u00e0 Yerry Mina ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t &lsquo;n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n&rsquo; trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ra s\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng Samuel Umtiti, Gerard Pique hay Mascherano, Mina \u0111\u00e0nh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn &lsquo;\u0111\u00e1nh b\u00f3ng&rsquo; b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Barca, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca m\u01a1\u0301i chi\u00eau m\u00f4\u0323 tha\u0300nh c\u00f4ng trung v\u00ea\u0323 Clement Lenglet, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Mina c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean u \u00e1m h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, M.U \u0111\u00e3 &lsquo;\u0111\u00e1nh h\u01a1i&rsquo; v\u00e0 li\u00ean l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi Mina. Theo \u0111\u00e0i RMC, Mourinho \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n n\u00e0y, v\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p>S\u1edf h\u1eefu chi\u1ec1u cao 1m94 c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018 v\u1eeba qua v\u1edbi 3 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do gi\u00fap HLV Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c, Man \u0111\u1ecf \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb chia tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd Mateo Darmian. Darmian ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu M.U kh\u00f4ng gia h\u1ea1n, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n b\u00e1n anh s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1edfi v\u1eady, Mourinho c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Darmian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p r\u1eddi CLB, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Hi\u1ec7n Napoli \u0111ang r\u1ea5t k\u1ebft ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U, v\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Aurelio De Laurentiis c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-tri-gia-100-trieu-euro-cua-mu-muon-gia-nhap-chelsea-172-192026.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/9/muc-tieu-tri-gia-100-trieu-euro-cua-mu-muon-gia-nhap-chelsea.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/muc-tieu-tri-gia-100-trieu-euro-cua-mu-muon-gia-nhap-chelsea-172-192026.html\">M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro c\u1ee7a MU mu\u1ed1n gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea</span><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Sergej Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, t\u1edd Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn The Blues \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi HLV...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-sao-tre-mu-nen-duoc-mourinho-trao-co-hoi-mua-toi-172-192015.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/3-sao-tre-mu-nen-duoc-mourinho-trao-co-hoi-mua-toi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-sao-tre-mu-nen-duoc-mourinho-trao-co-hoi-mua-toi-172-192015.html\">3 sao tr\u1ebb MU n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nMan United \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n t\u1eeb l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o Carrington. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 sao tr\u1ebb x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-dua-ra-gia-ban-tien-ve-tony-kroos-180-192017.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/clb-real-madrid-dua-ra-gia-ban-tien-ve-tony-kroos.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/clb-real-madrid-dua-ra-gia-ban-tien-ve-tony-kroos-180-192017.html\">CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u01b0a ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ho\u00e0ng gia TBN m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111\u00e3 ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toni Kroos cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c anh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1633","checkdouble":"192031"},{"date":"23:16 25/07","title":"Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Monaco \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Golovin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA Moscow, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea, Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea, Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/xac-nhan-hang-hot-golovin-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Golovin c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Golovin c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Nga. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea-172-191470.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin</span>, Juventus, M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga, song Monaco m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Monaco, anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 6.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Monaco.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Golovin ch\u1ecdn Monaco thay v\u00ec Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c thay v\u00ec Chelsea ho\u1eb7c Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Golovin la cau thu choi hay nhat ben phia Nga khi ghi 1 ban va kien tao 2 ban khac\" title=\"Golovin l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Nga khi ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 2 b\u00e0n kh\u00e1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMonaco v\u00e0 CSKA \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Golovin. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, song \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec Golovin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a CLB ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, \u1edf Monaco kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Chelsea. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Stamford Bridge, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1632","checkdouble":"192032"},{"date":"23:35 25/07","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u sao U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/20/hlv-park-hang-seo-yeu-cau-sao-u23-viet-nam-giam-can.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m PVF, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 ra ch\u1ec9 th\u1ecb y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ph\u1ea3i l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c r\u01b0\u1edbn.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Park Hang Seo y\u00eau c\u1ea7u H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-yeu-cau-Ha-Duc-Chinh-giam-can-hinh-anh.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110\u1ee9c Chinh ph\u1ea3i m\u1eb7c \u00e1o d\u00e0y nh\u1eb1m l\u00e0m gi\u1ea3m tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3. \u1ea2nh: Webthethao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 25/7, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra s\u00e2n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018. \u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, do ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n s\u1ed1 n\u00ean HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1eadp nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p nh\u00f3m c\u1ef1 li ng\u1eafn v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp n\u00e0y, HLV Park Hang Seo c\u0169ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh nhanh ch\u00f3ng gi\u1ea3m c\u00e2n. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n t\u1edbi t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 cho ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00fa Th\u1ecd m\u1eb7c \u00e1o m\u01b0a l\u00f3t ph\u00eda trong khi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed1t ch\u00e1y l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ee1 th\u1eeba nh\u1eb1m gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 c\u00e2n theo nh\u01b0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 th\u1ea7y Park y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 b\u1edfi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u0103ng c\u00e2n trong th\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u00ean v\u1ec1 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng pha b\u1ee9t ph\u00e1 qu\u00e3ng ng\u1eafn t\u1ed1t. Do v\u1eady, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y Park r\u1ea5t quan t\u00e2m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0 \u0110\u1ee9c Chinh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 7 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7y Park tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp cho ASIAD 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean anh s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Indonesia v\u00e0o trung tu\u1ea7n th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192032.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-lo-ngai-ve-kha-nang-tien-xa-cua-olympic-viet-nam-168-192032.html\">Chuy\u00ean gia lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn xa c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/16/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/asiad-2018-viet-nam-de-qua-vong-bang-kho-tho-vong-knockout-168-192005.html\">ASIAD 2018: Vi\u1ec7t Nam d\u1ec5 qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, kh\u00f3 th\u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out</span><br>\r\nK\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a 26 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n tham d\u1ef1. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1631","checkdouble":"192033"},{"date":"23:56 25/07","title":"Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/quang-hai-doi-mua-chien-dau-truoc-ngay-hoi-quan-cung-dt-olympic-viet-nam.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ASIAD 2018, Quang H\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i m\u01b0a c\u00f9ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i k\u1ecbch chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018.\r\n</h2><div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Quang Hai va Van Hau khoi dong truoc tran dau giua Ha Noi vs Binh Duong.\" title=\"Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 V\u0103n H\u1eadu kh\u