-1 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u1ed1i d\u00e0i k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vuot-sieu-pham-cua-cong-phuong-quang-hai-dan-dau-danh-sach-ban-thang-dep-vong-11-168-187799.html\">T\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m C\u1ea7u v\u1ed3ng tuy\u1ebft, Quang H\u1ea3i d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00f2ng 11</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/truc-tiep-ha-noi-vs-khanh-hoa-19h00-ngay-36-vleague-2018-372-187654.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i 4-0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a (KT): Quang H\u1ea3i s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft, \u0111\u1ed9c c\u00f4 c\u1ea7u b\u1ea1i l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng to</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/quang-hai-chan-thuong-ha-noi-gap-kho-truoc-chuyen-lam-khach-slna-291-187231.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch SLNA</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/quang-hai-tien-dung-hai-con-nguoi-mot-so-phan-167-187066.html\">Quang H\u1ea3i &ndash; Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng: Hai con ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-khien-quang-hai-sa-sut-tai-vleague-2018-291-187014.html\">L\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Quang H\u1ea3i sa s\u00fat t\u1ea1i V-League 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1630","checkdouble":"192034"},{"date":"05:24 26/07","title":"X\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: H\u00e0ng hot Golovin t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/xac-nhan-hang-hot-golovin-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Monaco \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Golovin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o CSKA Moscow, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, t\u1eeb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m, ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea, Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Chelsea, Monaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/xac-nhan-hang-hot-golovin-tim-duoc-ben-do-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Golovin c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Monaco v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Golovin c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tuy\u1ec3n Nga. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a anh gi\u00fap ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga v\u00e0o t\u1edbi t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea-172-191470.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Golovin</span>, Juventus, M.U v\u00e0 Arsenal l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga, song Monaco m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonaco mua Aleksandr Golovin th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111ang tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Monaco, anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3i qua cu\u1ed9c ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 6.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed3i k\u1ebft. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Monaco.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do Golovin ch\u1ecdn Monaco thay v\u00ec Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Vadim Vasilyev x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Monaco chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Golovin, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c thay v\u00ec Chelsea ho\u1eb7c Juventus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Golovin la cau thu choi hay nhat ben phia Nga khi ghi 1 ban va kien tao 2 ban khac\" title=\"Golovin l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hay nh\u1ea5t b\u00ean ph\u00eda Nga khi ghi 1 b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 2 b\u00e0n kh\u00e1c\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/thuc-hu-viec-cska-dong-y-ban-golovin-cho-chelsea.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Golovin t\u1edbi Monaco \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMonaco v\u00e0 CSKA \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Golovin. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i Chelsea th\u00ec Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, song \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn l\u00e0 Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec Golovin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a CLB ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y, \u1edf Monaco kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Golovin c\u0169ng nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Chelsea. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf Stamford Bridge, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Monaco\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1629","checkdouble":"192035"},{"date":"05:43 26/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Chelsea chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/17/thuc-hu-vu-chelsea-chi-45-trieu-bang-mua-trung-ve-cua-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Daniele Rugani, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Davide Torchia c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Rugani</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi sau khi \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Daniele Rugani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Daniele Rugani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/21/Chelsea-dam-phan-mua-Daniele-Rugani-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rugani</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-italia-len-45-trieu-bang-172-191927.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Daniele Rugani c\u1ee7a Juventus</span>, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 t\u1ea1i Empoli v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n 20 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Serie A, anh g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Juventus.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u Rugani, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed HLV Sarri c\u00f2n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea3 Gary Cahill v\u00e0 David Luiz \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u00f3n ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Rugani. Nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Chelsea c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00e0 32, 36 v\u00e0 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Rugani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Daniele Rugani, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Davide Torchia c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus tu choi ban Daniele Rugani cho Arsenal\" title=\"Juventus t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Daniele Rugani cho Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/7/chelsea-nang-gia-hoi-mua-trung-ve-nguoi-italia-len-45-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Chelsea h\u1ecfi mua Daniele Rugani\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Rugani, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. Chelsea c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Juventus, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n di\u1ec5n ra nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o, song c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Juventus kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain c\u1ee7a Juventus, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y Torchia ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: \u201cVi\u1ec7c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Higuain v\u00e0 Rugani kh\u00e1c h\u1eb3n nhau, m\u1ed7i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c kh\u00e1c nhau\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRugani v\u1eabn \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Juventus, nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea3 Juventus v\u00e0 Rugani, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1628","checkdouble":"192036"},{"date":"06:15 26/07","title":"Atletico Madrid c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Liverpool v\u00e0 Juventus v\u1ee5 Godin","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/4/21/atletico-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-liverpool-va-juventus-vu-godin.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Diego Godin, HLV Diego Simeone x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, song Atletico t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Juventus quan t\u00e2m Godin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 Diego Godin duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1986 l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Atletico v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 \u0110T Uruguay n\u1eefa, anh s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Diego Godin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Diego Godin h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/4/21/atletico-madrid-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-liverpool-va-juventus-vu-godin.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Godin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool v\u00e0 Juventus theo \u0111u\u1ed5i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, trung v\u1ec7 Godin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Godin, HLV Klopp nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. The Kop ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 20 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong/juve-sap-chieu-mo-trung-ve-khung-ve-lam-ban-voi-ronaldo-187-191540.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Godin</span>, HLV Massimiliano Allegri \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Andrea Barzagli v\u00e0 Giorgio Chiellini \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Daniele Rugani \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea quan t\u00e2m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Liverpool, Juventus ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 20 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu Godin. H\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Simeone n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Godin</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Diego Godin, HLV Diego Simeone x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn, song Atletico t\u1ef1 tin gi\u1eef th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Godin\" title=\"trung ve Godin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/5/mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-cua-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Diego Simeone n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Godin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cVi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 quen v\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00f3. N\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m t\u00f4i ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Godin v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Atletico c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn theo \u0111u\u1ed5i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng Atletico \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. Atletico \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Griezmann, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 tin c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Godin \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAtletico v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Gelson Martins ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00e0o m\u1eebng Gelson Martins \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Wanda Metropolitano, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi Atletico m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1627","checkdouble":"192037"},{"date":"06:19 26/07","title":"C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Mourinho n\u1ed5i \u0111i\u00ean, mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed1ng kh\u1ee9 Martial c\u00e0ng nhanh c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/14/cuc-nong-mourinho-noi-dien-muon-tong-khu-martial-cang-nhanh-cang-tot.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, HLV Jose Mourinho \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00f3n c\u1eadu con trai s\u1eafp sinh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho t\u1ee9c \u0111i\u00ean ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Martial&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh M.U \u0111ang c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho, MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"M\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi Mourinho, MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/14/Tin-chuyen-nhuong-hom-nay-ngay-247,-tin-chuyen-nhuong-he-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd r\u1eddi M.U \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 \u00fd r\u1eddi Los Angeles \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p, theo \u0111\u00f3 anh t\u1edbi Paris, n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Melanie Da Cruz s\u1eafp sinh c\u1eadu con trai. Ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea3n doanh c\u1ee7a M.U ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi AC Milan di\u1ec5n ra.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Telegraph Sport , Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Martial th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n, \u00f4ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a cho ph\u00e9p nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1eabn t\u1ef1 \u00fd r\u1eddi \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Telegraph Sport, kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Martial c\u00f3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f9ng M.U tham gia chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa hay kh\u00f4ng. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa anh v\u00e0 Mourinho tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m Martial. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chot-thoi-diem-tottenham-va-mu-trao-doi-bom-tan-172-191994.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Alderweireld l\u1ea5y Martial</span>. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU b\u00e1n Anthony Martial l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn mua th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Fred v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0111a n\u0103ng Dalot. HLV Jose Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho\" title=\"Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/man-united-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-nguoi-thua-cua-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, TTCN r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 Mourinho mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu Martial ra \u0111i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Bale v\u00e0 Willian \u0111ang l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1626","checkdouble":"192038"},{"date":"06:46 26/07","title":"H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a John Stones khi\u1ebfn Pep m\u1eebng r\u01a1i n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/26/hanh-dong-nay-cua-john-stones-khien-pep-mung-roi-nuoc-mat.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>John Stones t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">John Stones c\u00f9ng Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 John Stones l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man City. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Nicolas Otamendi l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man xanh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"John Stones t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"John Stones t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/10/John-Stones-tap-trung-cung-Man-City-som-hon-du-kien-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stones c\u00f9ng Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Stones t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0, anh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Harry Magui v\u00e0 Kyle Walker l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJohn Stones kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 anh c\u00f2n cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Anh, Stones \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Man City \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>John Stones tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">John Stones \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018, theo d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Arsenal \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"John Stones tro lai Man City som hon du kien\" title=\"John Stones tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/hanh-dong-nay-cua-john-stones-khien-pep-mung-roi-nuoc-mat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>John Stones tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Kompany c\u0169ng \u0111ang trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 sau World Cup 2018 th\u00ec Pep ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n trong tay 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 bao g\u1ed3m Nicolas Otamendi v\u00e0 Aymeric Laporte.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, John Stones t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Man City s\u1edbm h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i c\u00f3 2 tu\u1ea7n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 c\u1ef1u sao Everton s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 g\u1eb7p Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nR\u00f5 r\u00e0ng s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Stones khi\u1ebfn Pep r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng b\u1edfi \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng cho th\u1ea5y anh r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1625","checkdouble":"192039"},{"date":"16:00 25/07","title":"V\u00ec Man City, Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Kante v\u00e0o tay Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/15/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ea5t Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0o tay Man City, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Express \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man City chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Miralem Pjanic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Pep Guardiola r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n mua m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho David Silva, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 32 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante thay Pjanic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante thay Pjanic h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/24/Juventus-muon-mua-Kante-thay-Pjanic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Pjanic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Jorginho l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Man xanh, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia v\u00e0o tay Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh v\u00e0 Italia, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sau-mahrez-man-city-sap-co-them-bom-tan-100-trieu-euro-172-191834.html\" target=\"_blank\">Man City mu\u1ed1n mua Miralem Pjanic</span> c\u1ee7a Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Pep \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pjanic v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Man xanh mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Pjanic ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. M\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i anh ghi t\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 15 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mua Kante thay Pjanic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ea5t Miralem Pjanic v\u00e0o tay Man City, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Express \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kante\" title=\"Kante\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/15/juventus-mua-kante-neu-mat-pjanic-vao-tay-man-city.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Kante thay Pjanic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Kante, song Juventus v\u1eabn tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u00e1n Pjanic \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Kante, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi 100 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Juventus th\u00ec PSG c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kante, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed Mbappe c\u00f2n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n PSG mua c\u1ef1u sao Leicester. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Kante kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec7n \u0111i hay \u1edf c\u1ee7a Anh ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o Chelsea.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1624","checkdouble":"191995"},{"date":"15:26 25/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng 19h00 ng\u00e0y 25/7 (C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/ha-noi-vs-binh-duong-ban-ket-cup-quoc-gia-viet-nam-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 25/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eeba ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t c\u01a1n kh\u00e1t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-1 h\u00f4m 21/7 v\u1eeba qua, \u1edf v\u00f2ng 20 V.League 2018. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Ti\u1ebfn Linh, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u1ea1o c\u1ed9i nh\u01b0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i c\u0169ng c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng y\u00ean t\u00e2m cho BHL \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t Th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 L\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean t\u00e2m ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n h\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018 cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Qu\u1ed1c n\u1ed9i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-ha-noi-vs-binh-duong-19h00-ngay-257-cup-quoc-gia-viet-nam-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch V.League ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee3i 'ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1eb9p' \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC gi\u01b0\u01a1ng cao, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac Quang H\u1ea3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0o c\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh l\u00ean Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00ed do g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh, nh\u1eb1m d\u1eabn l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 5/9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang s\u1ee9c, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111\u1ea3 b\u1ea1i c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng V.League, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 B.B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng k\u1ebf s\u00e1ch, chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt g\u00ec \u0111i ch\u0103ng n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea5y tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC b\u1ecb Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a, b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i, c\u00f2n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp - m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00f2n. B\u1edfi th\u1ebf, kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC ch\u1ee7 quan \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n>>> Xem th\u00eam: Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: V\u0103n C\u00f4ng, Duy M\u1ea1nh, \u0110\u00ecnh Tr\u1ecdng, V\u0103n H\u1eadu, V\u0103n Ki\u00ean, Moses, H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng, Quang H\u1ea3i, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft, Th\u00e0nh L\u01b0\u01a1ng, Samson.<br>\r\nB\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng: T\u1ea5n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Thanh Th\u1ea3o, H.T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Xu\u00e2n Lu\u00e2n, Anh T\u00e0i, L.T\u1ea5n T\u00e0i, Onyelonu, Ti\u1ebfn Linh, Ho\u00e0ng Max, Rabo Ali, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1623","checkdouble":"191996"},{"date":"17:04 25/07","title":"HLV Emery ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a th\u00eam 1 ng\u00f4i sao v\u1ec1 Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/hlv-emery-tiet-lo-muon-dua-them-1-ngoi-sao-ve-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt, theo Sport Bild, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ante Rebic \u0111ang g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ante Rebic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Eintracht Frankfurt. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 \u0111\u00e3 ghi 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/17/MU-muon-mua-Ante-Rebic-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Rebic \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Ante Rebic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 2 c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T Croatia, anh lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a HLV Dalic. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Rebic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Croatia v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Ante Rebic nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0110\u1ee9c, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea1i gia c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 MU, Arsenal, Tottenham v\u00e0 Napoli \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Rebic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Ante Rebic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt, theo Sport Bild, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ante Rebic ghi ban o dau hiep hai mo ti so cho Croatia.\" title=\"Ante Rebic ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 cho Croatia.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-247-mu-nham-sao-tuyen-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU mu\u1ed1n chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Ante Rebic\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Fredi Bobic c\u1ee7a Eintracht Frankfurt th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Eintracht Frankfurt, song r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Rebic \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t, t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Sport Bild, M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Rebic, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf m\u1edbi chi 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Fred v\u00e0 Dalot.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1622","checkdouble":"191997"},{"date":"15:34 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dortmund vs Benfica 7h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-dortmund-vs-benfica-7h00-ngay-267-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dortmund vs Benfica l\u00fac 7h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dortmund vs Benfica 7h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Dortmund vs Benfica 7h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Dortmund-vs-Benfica.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Dortmund vs Benfica</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Dortmund vs Benfica: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Dortmund \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i ICC\u00a02018 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i 2 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh l\u00e0 Man City (1-0) v\u00e0 Liverpool (3-1).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 3 t\u1ea1i\u00a0ICC 2018 g\u1eb7p Benfica - \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u1edd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i gia trong bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u00e0 th\u00f4i - Dortmund l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn Dortmund kh\u00f4ng an to\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDortmund t\u1eebng th\u1eafng Benfica 4-0 \u1edf Champions League c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i n\u0103m. Tuy nhi\u00ean l\u00fac n\u00e0y Benfica h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u0110N mua b\u00e1n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Benfica thu v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 15,38 tri\u1ec7u euro\u00a0 t\u1eeb vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 chi ra 28,7 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ec3 mua t\u00e2n binh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQuan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, c\u00e1c g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t m\u1edbi nh\u01b0 Joao Carvalho, Andre Horta hay Raul Jimenez \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Benfica \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla d\u00f9 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u: Hai \u0111\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p nhau 2 l\u1ea7n \u1edf Champions League 2016/17, Benfica th\u1eafng 1-0 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 thua 0-4 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn<br>\r\nDortmund: Marwin Hitz; Toljan, Toprak, Zagadou, Schmelzer; Pulisic, Gotze, Nuri Sahin, Schurrle; Isak.<br>\r\nBenfica: Vlachodimos; Andre Almeida, Conti, Jardel, Grimaldo, Fejsa, Pizzi, Fernandes, Salvio, Rafa Silva, Castillo.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1621","checkdouble":"191998"},{"date":"15:50 25/07","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma vs Tottenham 09h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (ICC 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/25/nhan-dinh-roma-vs-tottenham-09h00-ngay-267-icc-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma vs Tottenham l\u00fac 09h00 ng\u00e0y 26/7 (Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup ICC 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma vs Tottenham 09h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma vs Tottenham 09h00 ng\u00e0y 267 ICC 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/25/Roma-vs-Tottenham.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Roma vs Tottenham</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Roma vs Tottenham: 1-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 1 n\u0103m, AS Roma v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ea1i\u00a0ICC c\u0169ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.\u00a0K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Serie A th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 3-2 d\u00f9 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 n\u00e0y, AS\u00a0Roma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eb1m c\u1eeda tr\u00ean, ch\u1eb3ng ph\u1ea3i do Spurs sa s\u00fat m\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n nhi\u1ec1u do Tottenham thi\u1ebfu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n1 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, HLV Pochettino c\u00f3 trong tay \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u00f4ng m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1eeba tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018. Danh s\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Lloris, Alli, Kane, Kieran Trippier, Danny Rose, Toby Alderweireld, Jan Vertonghen, Eric Dier v\u00e0 Mousa Dembele.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 v\u00e0i tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t \u00edt \u1ecfi c\u0169ng tham d\u1ef1 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh nh\u01b0 Davinson Sanchez, Christian Eriksen hay Son Heung-min \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch sang M\u1ef9, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p AS Roma v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng mai, HLV Pochettino nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 hay d\u00e0n sao tr\u1ebb.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u201cG\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng\u201d th\u00ec AS Roma \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 2 m\u00e0n th\u1eed l\u1eeda. Do \u0111\u00f3 x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00dd \u0103n \u0111\u1ee9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Premier League. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n- Hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p nhau t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 2 tr\u1eadn, AS Roma th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 1.<br>\r\n- T\u1ea1i ICC Cup, AS Roma th\u1eafng 1, h\u00f2a 0, thua 1. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed8I H\u00ccNH D\u1ef0 KI\u1ebeN<br>\r\nAS Roma (4-1-2-3): Mirante; Juan, Manolas, Kolarov, Karsdorp; Gonalons; Pastore, Cristante; Schick, Kluivert, Dzeko.<br>\r\nTottenham (4-2-3-1): Vorm; Sanchez, Foyth, Aurier, Davies; Wanyama, Oakley-Boothe; Lamela, Son Heung-min, Lucas; Llorente.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1620","checkdouble":"191999"}]}